name: IQClientApi
summary: This pod will serve as a library to get and set data, to and from the datacenter's api. (Api->Api)
description:
A framework that will serve the same purpose as the framework "swagger-codegen's" generated code, would have.
This framework does not generate code but only speaks to the given IQ datacentes endpoints.
Swift_4.1, IOS_11.3, Xcode_9.3(9E145)
